  "source_file": "2cc59d.ot2.apiv2.py",
  "intent_precise": "SuperScript III: qRT-PCR Prep with CSV File: Using temp_plate (labware, slot Starting), res12 (reservoir, slot 3), res (reservoir, slot 11), greiner_plate (plate, slot 2). With temperature module. (1) Pause: \nRefill Tipracks\n (2) Transfer 270\u00b5L from source to destination. (3) Transfer 150\u00b5L from source to destination. (4) Transfer 126\u00b5L from source to destination. (5) Transfer 30\u00b5L from source to destination. (6) Mix 5 times at 300\u00b5L. (7) Transfer 150\u00b5L from source to destination. (8) Mix 5 times at 300\u00b5L. (9) Transfer 14\u00b5L from source to destination. (10) Mix 3 times at 20\u00b5L. (11) Transfer 14\u00b5L from source to destination. (12) Mix 3 times at 20\u00b5L. (13) Transfer 14\u00b5L from patient_samples A1 to destination. (14) Transfer 120\u00b5L from source to destination. (15) Transfer 120\u00b5L from source to destination. (16) Transfer 120\u00b5L from source to destination. (17) Mix 2 times at 300\u00b5L. (18) Transfer 120\u00b5L from source to destination. (19) Mix 2 times at 300\u00b5L. (20) Pause: Place Greiner plate on plate warmer at 37C for 30 minutes,\n                 Then select \"Resume\" on the Opentrons App. (21) Transfer 200\u00b5L from source to destination. (22) Pause: Place Costar plate on plate warmer at 37C for 30 minutes,\n                 Then select \"Resume\" on the Opentrons App. (23) Transfer 100\u00b5L from source to destination. (24) Transfer 260\u00b5L from source to destination. (25) Transfer 260\u00b5L from source to destination. (26) Pause: Washing complete. Add 10mL TMB to column 3 of the reservoir\n                Select \"Resume\" on the Opentrons app to continue (27) Transfer 100\u00b5L from source to destination. (28) Pause: Incubate Costar plate in the dark for 15 minutes at room\n                temperature. Place 5mL stop solution in column 4\n                of the reservoir.\n                Select \"Resume\" on the Opentrons app to continue (29) Transfer 50\u00b5L from source to destination.",
  "intent_concise": "Perform 18 liquid transfers. (volumes 14\u00b5L-300\u00b5L)",
  "intent": "For this SuperScript III qRT-PCR prep protocol, you'll be working with the temp_plate in the starting slot, res12 in slot 3, res in slot 11, and the greiner_plate in slot 2 with the temperature module active. Start by refilling the tipracks, then perform the initial reagent transfers of 270\u00b5L, 150\u00b5L, 126\u00b5L, and 30\u00b5L followed by mixing 5 times at 300\u00b5L volume. Continue with the subsequent 150\u00b5L transfer and mixing, then add 14\u00b5L aliquots twice with 3x mixing at 20\u00b5L each time, followed by transferring 14\u00b5L from patient_samples A1. Complete the setup with four 120\u00b5L transfers, mixing 2 times at 300\u00b5L after the third and fourth transfers, then incubate the Greiner plate at 37\u00b0C for 30 minutes before proceeding with the 200\u00b5L transfer, another 37\u00b0C incubation for the Costar plate, and finishing with 100\u00b5L, two 260\u00b5L transfers, TMB addition to column 3, 100\u00b5L transfer, 15-minute dark incubation, stop solution addition to column 4, and final 50\u00b5L transfer.",
